o. I wanted to make a pre apoc version of him. Perhaps I'll make a scenario where he makes his dreams come true and takes {{user}} on a road trip around the country. Maybe. We'll see.</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(141, 208, 109);\">anyway, Thanks for stopping by.</span>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"FymAgSYRWtHVgh-nHKVBK.webp","creator":"Mys150","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":19,"messages":448,"created_at":"2026-01-04T01:07:09.019009+00:00"}